testsuite.name: org.apache.openwhisk.common.ForcibleSemaphoreTests

testcase.name: ForcableSemaphore should not allow to acquire, force or release negative amounts of permits
ForcableSemaphore should allow to acquire the defined amount of permits only
ForcableSemaphore should allow to release permits again
ForcableSemaphore should allow to force permits, delaying the acceptance of 'usual' permits until all of forced permits are released
ForcableSemaphore should not give away more permits even under concurrent load
